Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.16,0:00:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everyone, Kaleido Star is about to start.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.16,0:00:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When you watch Kaleido Star,\Nplease keep your room brightly lit,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.87,0:00:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and sit as far from the TV as you can.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.76,0:00:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, well, well. Do you\Nhave anybody you admire?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.15,0:00:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Someone you think is cool,\Nsomeone wonderful,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.96,0:00:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}or someone you wish you could be like.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.26,0:00:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To me, that is Miss Layla. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.34,0:00:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is a chance to maybe appear\Non stage with the person I admire.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.10,0:00:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have to get this chance by\Nall means! I have to! I have to!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.03,0:01:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yaritai koto wa nani {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.63,0:01:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sou kikareru tabi {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.48,0:01:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Aoi sora miageta {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.27,0:01:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kotae wa only my heart {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.57,0:01:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Honto ni daiji na kotoba\Nwa kantan ni wa iwanai{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.10,0:01:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hikari ga yubisasu\Nbasho e to hashiridasu yo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.14,0:01:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dakishimetai mono nara\Nnakitai hodo mune ni aru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.30,0:01:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Egakitsuzukete yuku kitto take it someday{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.24,0:01:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shiroi kumo ga nagareru\Nchiheisen no mukou ni{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.29,0:02:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Naranderu mirai wa itsumo soba ni aru kara{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.94,0:02:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"A Hot, Amazing, New Production."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.90,0:02:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, it ended...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.67,0:02:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my first leading role.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.99,0:02:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.13,0:02:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.95,0:02:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iyaan...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.71,0:02:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iyaan... Iyaan...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.72,0:02:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.95,0:02:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ian! Ian!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.99,0:02:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ian?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.88,0:02:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Ian, in the flesh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.24,0:02:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.16,0:02:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By any chance, are you talking about Ian\Nwho co-starred with Miss Layla in the movie?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.13,0:02:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.58,0:02:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not particularly his fan. Right, Sora?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.75,0:03:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm not particularly his...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.19,0:03:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.91,0:03:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, but what kind of help?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.96,0:03:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know you meant this kind of help.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.49,0:03:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There he is. There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.62,0:03:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where, where?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.33,0:03:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is real!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.74,0:03:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An amazing million dollar smile!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.91,0:03:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,America's lover.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.94,0:03:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't imagine anyone other than Layla
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.11,0:03:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,playing the main role for the next movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.96,0:03:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, this is the first\Nmovie that I'm going to produce.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.09,0:03:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already told you\Nformally that I'm not interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.11,0:03:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know how you feel, Layla.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.82,0:03:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There it is again, the million dollar smile!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.96,0:03:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She is under pressure,\Nand puzzled over what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.96,0:03:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Kalos, I want you to persuade her, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.93,0:03:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you understand that coming\Nto my place is the best choice for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.55,0:04:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead, please persuade her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.73,0:04:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Layla, I think you should go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.81,0:04:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I think I should.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.71,0:04:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What! So, okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.47,0:04:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bravo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.12,0:04:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.37,0:04:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About Layla, she said okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.77,0:04:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.40,0:04:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good-bye, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.91,0:04:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, good-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.33,0:04:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.16,0:04:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. Wha--?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.88,0:04:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Uh. Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.99,0:04:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.21,0:04:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you said "go,"\Nwhat did you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.76,0:04:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're supposed to go to see the\Nstage equipment for a new production.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.39,0:04:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding! No one told me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.37,0:04:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just invited yourself to follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.77,0:04:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.58,0:04:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.33,0:04:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a profound\Nreason why we're doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.12,0:04:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop embarrassing yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.48,0:04:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.90,0:04:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's perfect. You should come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.05,0:04:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.36,0:04:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why... me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.13,0:04:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Layla!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.77,0:04:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Mr. Ian also followed them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.89,0:04:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.03,0:04:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I would like to go, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.06,0:05:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still in a trial stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.59,0:05:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, please take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.47,0:05:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what took you so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.88,0:05:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.46,0:05:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the equipment for ropewalking\Nin the new production, Arabian Nights.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.63,0:05:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the climax, you will perform\Naction scenes on top of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.81,0:05:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow... It sounds amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.93,0:05:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, after all, it's just ropewalking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.48,0:05:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing new to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.24,0:05:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the other hand, my next\Nmovie will be a little different.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.61,0:05:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It moved!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.10,0:05:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the time you perform, more\Ncomplicated moves will be possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.29,0:05:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.93,0:05:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand, Layla.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.35,0:05:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I'll use a ship in my movie, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.06,0:05:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.15,0:05:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare a ship that I can use for my movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.64,0:05:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep. A big one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.23,0:06:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is pretty tricky.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.23,0:06:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to have a one-on-one\Nfight with a bandit on top of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.68,0:06:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, when you perform before the audience,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.04,0:06:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the ship will be enveloped in flames.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.09,0:06:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.09,0:06:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Fire?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.51,0:06:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is ridiculous, Layla.\NI think you should stop--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.52,0:06:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.20,0:06:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire, fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.39,0:06:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Layla gets excited about\Nscenes that have fire in them!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.57,0:06:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Order gunpowder!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.41,0:07:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri, let's start practicing immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.56,0:07:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems I'm not the one you are\Ngoing to have a fight scene with.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.31,0:07:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.37,0:07:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I wonder if they're going\Nto audition for my opponent's role.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.72,0:07:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, our main sponsor Mr. Kenneth\Nalready nominated the person, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.05,0:07:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.74,0:07:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.26,0:07:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You and Sora will co-star in\Nthe climax of Arabian Nights.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.83,0:07:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.04,0:07:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to co-star with... Miss Layla...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.83,0:07:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both you and Kenneth\Nmust be out of your minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.74,0:07:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the Little Mermaid\Ncould hardly be called a success.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.24,0:07:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Mr. Kenneth says if you\Nand Sora are going to co-star,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.44,0:07:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he wouldn't mind doubling the budget.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.47,0:07:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.39,0:07:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.14,0:07:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.98,0:07:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have confidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.54,0:07:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.96,0:07:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't have confidence,\Nexcuse yourself from this role.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.38,0:07:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Kenneth will understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.70,0:07:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kalos, she cannot do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.61,0:07:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's pitiful to pressure her\Nmore than what we're doing now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.54,0:07:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyhow, it's a bit too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.07,0:08:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's ask the scriptwriter to rewrite the\Naction scenes using Yuri instead of Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.06,0:08:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Kenneth will be very disappointed,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.97,0:08:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but we have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.25,0:08:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.92,0:08:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla, I want to try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.01,0:08:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.22,0:08:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me do this, Miss Layla.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.25,0:08:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.44,0:08:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.85,0:08:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.89,0:08:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still a newcomer. How rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.50,0:08:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Layla?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.75,0:08:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still don't have confidence, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.68,0:08:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have confidence\Nand you still want to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.23,0:08:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my God!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.41,0:08:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please test me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.03,0:08:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're just going to \Ngive up after the test,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.14,0:08:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you should resign now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.97,0:08:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a nuisance if you're going to prepare\Nyourself with a half-baked attitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.82,0:08:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.87,0:08:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me know when you make up your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.15,0:08:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Layla!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.44,0:08:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.46,0:08:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should make up your own mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.51,0:08:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ropewalking on a rolling ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.94,0:08:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that sounds tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.42,0:09:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even Miss Layla fell from the rope.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.55,0:09:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, have you ever done ropewalking?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.28,0:09:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.35,0:09:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Naegino!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.87,0:09:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're playing circus again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.40,0:09:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.22,0:09:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, you're weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.05,0:09:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.84,0:09:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usually, people don't volunteer\Nfor that if that is all you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.18,0:09:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.83,0:09:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it was me, I'd definitely excuse myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.29,0:09:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, you're going to do it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.80,0:09:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Er... I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.46,0:09:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if it's impossible after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.84,0:09:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I went over budget because of\Nthe gunpowder I ordered for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.59,0:09:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From the beginning of the\Nmovie, there's fire, fire, fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.77,0:09:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To the end, the whole \Nmovie is fire, fire, fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.14,0:09:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think? Excited, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.48,0:09:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.00,0:09:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why does it have to be Sora? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.36,0:09:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why am I so concerned about her?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.41,0:09:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.85,0:09:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One day, it will be her\Nthe audience comes to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.97,0:10:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it seems like you\Nfinally made up your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.99,0:10:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ian...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.38,0:10:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Layla...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.74,0:10:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you find a wonderful leading actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.88,0:10:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank-- What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.49,0:10:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.81,0:10:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.56,0:10:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cancel the gunpowder.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.94,0:10:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't?! Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.52,0:10:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You need someone to talk to?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.66,0:10:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never felt this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.16,0:10:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.69,0:10:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about Sora, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.11,0:10:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She has something you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.42,0:10:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.50,0:10:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She takes chances.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.03,0:10:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.24,0:10:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, no one here at Kaleido Stage,\Nincluding myself, takes chances like she does.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.68,0:10:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.24,0:10:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.82,0:10:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what Kalos wants from her is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.82,0:10:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.40,0:10:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I will support your ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.74,0:11:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take me to Kaleido Stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.12,0:11:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.44,0:11:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.57,0:11:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end... do you think\NI should excuse myself from this role?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.59,0:11:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I told you to\Nmake up your own mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.04,0:11:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.65,0:11:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then... this time, I will...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.00,0:11:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.15,0:11:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.95,0:11:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kalos, let's have a test.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.85,0:11:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to take a test, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.71,0:11:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,about whether I can co-star with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.14,0:11:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I want you to decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.19,0:11:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.85,0:11:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The deadline is a week\Nfrom now. Is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.79,0:11:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.72,0:11:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I look forward to seeing your performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.52,0:11:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My performance?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.56,0:12:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna burn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.96,0:12:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or, it's more like I can't breathe...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.90,0:12:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.76,0:12:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm suffocating...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.98,0:12:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna die.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.72,0:12:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zzzz... Zzzz...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.14,0:12:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First thing in the morning,\Nand you still treat me terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.22,0:12:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which is more terrible?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.44,0:12:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you, I dreamt\NI was burning to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.25,0:12:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will teach you one good thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.14,0:12:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.01,0:12:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In a story like Arabian Nights,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.15,0:12:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you should say you're "covered in flames"\Ninstead of saying "burned to death."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.84,0:12:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.86,0:12:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it. Very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.84,0:12:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at the front.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.13,0:12:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.04,0:12:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought, Sora has a talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.67,0:12:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, she does.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.87,0:12:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she still has a long way to go\Nbefore she can co-star with Miss Layla.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.22,0:12:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you're getting\Ncomfortable with ropewalking,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.67,0:12:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,let's try rolling the\Nship a little without the bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.27,0:12:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What! Already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.83,0:12:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have much time left.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.11,0:13:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, we have to keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.19,0:13:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.80,0:13:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.87,0:13:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this were a real stage, \Nyou'd be barbecued.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.04,0:13:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Barbecued?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.53,0:13:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.77,0:13:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, she's doing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.08,0:13:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's she doing, Ken?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.40,0:13:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To tell the truth, she has a long way to go,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.46,0:13:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but her maneuvers are getting bold.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.73,0:13:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think she is getting \Nused to using the rope.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.77,0:13:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm... That's my girl, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.24,0:13:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Mia, Anna.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.33,0:13:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you finish your lessons today?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.01,0:13:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.64,0:13:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you have a short break?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.70,0:13:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.75,0:13:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I want to practice a little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.42,0:13:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.91,0:14:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Sarah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.37,0:14:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, we're going.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.65,0:14:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.58,0:14:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To overcome your weak points.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.87,0:14:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My... weak points?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.18,0:14:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.04,0:14:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Katsu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.01,0:14:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The resolved mind has no cares!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.82,0:14:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.24,0:14:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Taurus's star cluster, Pleiades.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.19,0:14:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--And this star is Aldebaran.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.21,0:14:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.16,0:14:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we are in Aldebaran now!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.63,0:14:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.53,0:14:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though your body burns on\Nthis earth, you don't feel the heat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.03,0:14:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.06,0:14:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.91,0:14:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not afraid of the flame.\NWe're not afraid of the flame!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.24,0:14:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your weak point is your\Nfear of being barbequed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.21,0:14:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.25,0:14:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You overcame that fear, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.71,0:14:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're not afraid of \Nfalling into the flame,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.49,0:14:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you should be able to move more boldly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.41,0:14:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.53,0:14:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I'm misunderstanding something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.82,0:15:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh, no. Not at all.\N- -Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.19,0:15:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.23,0:15:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good. Then, good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.76,0:15:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.17,0:15:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost time to switch with Miss Layla.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.83,0:15:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.24,0:15:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're getting better, don't you think?\NYou're getting quite stable.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.70,0:15:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.86,0:15:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Ken.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.62,0:15:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.80,0:15:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not doing well?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.94,0:15:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I started getting ideas \Non how to do it right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.04,0:15:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.03,0:15:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.00,0:15:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But even if I manage to\Nbe able to do ropewalking,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.89,0:15:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure if I can pass the test.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.48,0:15:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I look forward to seeing your performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.91,0:15:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can do this much in this short time...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.89,0:15:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think Miss Layla will\Nacknowledge your performance?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.98,0:15:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.51,0:16:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I think something is missing...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.04,0:16:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.73,0:16:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.01,0:16:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.28,0:16:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My locker won't open!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.53,0:16:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.59,0:16:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who'd do something like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.56,0:16:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you do it yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.56,0:16:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you get hurt, you can, like,\Nget out of taking Miss Layla's test.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.49,0:16:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you two did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.67,0:16:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.06,0:16:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Diabolo...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.59,0:16:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Diabolo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.06,0:16:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.34,0:16:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's like, happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.95,0:16:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My performance... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.44,0:16:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pushing yourself too hard\Nwill not produce a good result.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.45,0:16:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you have a break?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.84,0:16:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a bath...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.11,0:16:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.58,0:16:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you worry, you\Nshould hasten to take a bath...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.35,0:16:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.01,0:16:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a bath...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.45,0:16:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora! Hey, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.86,0:16:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Fool, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.05,0:16:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.30,0:17:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your jump is too high!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.94,0:17:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.96,0:17:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.89,0:17:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look closely at your diabolo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.84,0:17:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good! Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.07,0:17:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time to switch.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.28,0:17:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.08,0:17:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally. Tomorrow is the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.71,0:17:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.90,0:17:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.97,0:17:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tomorrow... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.35,0:17:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My time for practice is over... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.92,0:17:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ken, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.34,0:17:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow, I will do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.28,0:18:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you want to practice a little more?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.77,0:18:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.56,0:18:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.31,0:18:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.35,0:18:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.67,0:18:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo! I've been waiting for you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.90,0:18:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Policeman.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.46,0:18:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? Excuse me, but aren't you the\Ndoctor who took care of my father?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.51,0:18:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I'm Kate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.69,0:18:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.96,0:18:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you dating?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.17,0:18:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.83,0:18:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.68,0:18:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're just childhood friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.85,0:18:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you mean when\Nyou said you've been waiting?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.79,0:18:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I consulted with Mr. Policeman,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.46,0:18:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he told me that Kate knows\Nsomeone who works at Marine Park.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.75,0:18:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.35,0:18:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All my family members are\Nfans of your Little Mermaid.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.89,0:18:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.08,0:18:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, this is a real one!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.55,0:18:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is it, Ken?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.97,0:18:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.38,0:19:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.63,0:19:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.83,0:19:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but it's almost time, I have to....
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.96,0:19:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.00,0:19:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.35,0:19:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if you managed to\Ndo this much in one week,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.43,0:19:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you did enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.72,0:19:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.72,0:19:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still think your last jump is too high.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.48,0:19:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to control yourself a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.12,0:19:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, of course, that's just like Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.43,0:19:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Certainly, it makes me nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.42,0:19:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're not afraid of falling into the flame,\Nyou should be able to move more boldly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.14,0:19:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.06,0:19:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not afraid of falling?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.41,0:19:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It may be okay to fall...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.15,0:19:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.23,0:20:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.82,0:20:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're amazing, Layla!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.52,0:20:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, next is Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.41,0:20:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.92,0:21:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then, next will be the finish! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.74,0:21:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sink or swim. {\i0}
